the sense of an ending is a 2016 american drama film written and directed by ritesh batra . the film stars jim broadbent , harriet palmer , harriet &lt;unk&gt; , and david broadbent . the film is based on julian barnes 's novel , the sense of an adaptation of julian barnes 's novel , the sense of an adaptation of julian barnes 's novel , the sense of an ending by julian barnes . the film was released on september 14 , 2015 .